dct_title_s: Marine Protected Areas, Channel Islands, California, 2004
dct_description_sm: This polygon shapefile represents the Channel Islands Marine Protected Areas. Pending Office of Administrative Law approval MPAs in effect as of April 9, 2003. This layer is part of a collection of data created by the California Department of Fish and Game.
This shapefile was prepared to make web and hardcopy documents for public distribution of the Channel Island Marine Protected Areas. This map should not be used for navigational purposes.
This file is not for navigational purposes.
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
